cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper involves the use of deep learning techniques for image segmentation and optimization, which are commonly associated with computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of cardiac magnetic resonance (CMR) also suggests a potential association with multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Additionally, the use of neural networks for feature tracking may also suggest a connection to neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
